		{
			dependencies: ["9005"]
			description: [
				"Gold rings set with gems provide meaningful stat bonuses. The §6Gold Ring§r offers stronger effects than iron or copper variants."
				""
				"Combine a §eGold Ingot§r with any gem at the §6Jeweler\u2019s Kit§r to craft a gold gem ring. Each gem type provides a different stat effect \u2014 experiment to find combinations that suit your playstyle."
				""
				"Netherite rings are the top tier, found in end-game loot or crafted with Netherite Ingots."
