		{
			dependencies: ["9002"]
			description: [
				"§bWizards§r is an RPG class mod focused on elemental spell casting through wands and staves."
				""
				"Pick up any §6Novice Wand§r to begin your wizard progression. Wands come pre-loaded with a basic spell."
				""
				"To unlock the full spell library, find a §6Wizard Tower§r in a village (added by §bGazebos§r) and use the §6Spell Binding Table§r to obtain your Spellbook."
				""
				"§eWizard§r villagers in these towers also sell wands and spell tomes."
