		{
			dependencies: ["9010"]
			description: [
				"The §6Tome of Arcane§r is the Wizards\u2019 core spellbook, focused on precise, single-target arcane spells."
				""
				"Unlock it at the §6Spell Binding Table§r in a §eWizard Tower§r village structure. Once you have the Tome equipped, you can bind specific arcane spells to your wand."
				""
				"Spells are cast using §6Runes§r as ammunition. The §6Spell Infinity§r enchantment removes the Rune cost once unlocked."
