		{
			dependencies: ["9011"]
			description: [
				"The §6Tome of Fire§r unlocks area-of-effect fire damage spells \u2014 ideal for clearing groups of enemies."
				""
				"Obtain it from the §6Spell Binding Table§r in a §eWizard Tower§r or trade with a §eWizard§r villager."
				""
				"Fire spells deal high burst damage but require careful positioning to avoid self-ignition. Equip §6Fire Resistance§r when experimenting with new fire spell combinations."
				""
				"The §6Spell Power§r enchantment increases fire spell damage, and §6Spell Haste§r improves cast speed."
