		{
			dependencies: ["9011"]
			description: [
				"The §6Tome of Frost§r unlocks ice and chill spells that hinder enemy movement and shield the caster."
				""
				"Frost spells are excellent for crowd control \u2014 slowing enemies with Slowness effects and creating ice barriers. They are particularly powerful in combination with faster weapons, giving you time to strike while the enemy is chilled."
				""
				"The §6Arcane Staff§r boosts spell range and power compared to standard wands. Seek one out from Wizard villagers or dungeon chests."
